prompt_text: Describe the moment in your life that you cherish the most.
content_text: So the cherish moment of my life is a day when I bought my pet at my house. That was a lovely day for me. It was very incredible and. Non forgettable. For me it's a memorable day, the time when I pick up my bed in my house. He was just two months old and that feeling was really awesome. I never forgot that as it was my first pet Ann. I really love him a lot. He's very adorable. Lovely. Anne does that Sandy smile makes makes my life more cherish and I never want to be separate from my pet.
